# Python lockfile is regenerated inside the Linux Docker image — see
# DEPLOY.md "Regenerating the Python lockfile". Committing a local
# (especially Anaconda/Windows) freeze pollutes it with host-specific
# file:// paths, so keep it local-only until you run the Docker regen.
requirements.lock
